  "text": "Research effort must also be focused on the development of diagnostic tools appropriate for wildlife species [CITATION_1] . The main drawback is that experimental research requires more funding than surveillance alone, and the former needs to be carried out by multidisciplinary scientific teams, which are scarce.",
